<h3>Claim your handle</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Claim your handle","zh":"认领你的句柄"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Keys are generated on your device, sealed by your passphrase. Grab <em>@you</em>, or stay completely anonymous.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Keys are generated on your device, sealed by your passphrase.","zh":"密钥在您的设备上生成，并由您的密码密封。"},{"en":"Grab @you, or stay completely anonymous.","zh":"抓住@you，或者保持完全匿名。"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Sync your people</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Sync your people","zh":"同步您的人员"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Your private key never leaves your device. Ekko only publishes the <em>public</em> key people need to reach you. It never uploads the key that opens your messages.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Your private key never leaves your device.","zh":"您的私钥永远不会离开您的设备。"},{"en":"Ekko only publishes the public key people need to reach you.","zh":"Ekko 仅发布人们联系您所需的公钥。"},{"en":"It never uploads the key that opens your messages.","zh":"它永远不会上传打开您的消息的密钥。"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Write where you already chat</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Write where you already chat","zh":"写下你们已经聊天的地方"}]},{"html_en":"<p>The mark sits at the end of the box. It names who it is sealing to, checks their key, and the words leave encrypted. In your browser today, in your keyboard next.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"The mark sits at the end of the box.","zh":"标记位于盒子的末端。"},{"en":"It names who it is sealing to, checks their key, and the words leave encrypted.","zh":"它会说出要密封的对象，检查他们的密钥，然后将这些单词加密。"},{"en":"In your browser today, in your keyboard next.","zh":"今天在您的浏览器中，接下来在您的键盘中。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>TWO WAYS TO USE IT</p>","sentences":[{"en":"TWO WAYS TO USE IT","zh":"两种使用方式"}]},{"html_en":"<h2>Claim a handle. Or stay a ghost.</h2>","sentences":[{"en":"Claim a handle.","zh":"索取句柄。"},{"en":"Or stay a ghost.","zh":"或者留下一个幽灵。"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>@you, everywhere</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"@you, everywhere","zh":"@你，无处不在"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Claim your handle once, link your socials, and add friends everywhere. They find your public key automatically. Every app you share becomes a sealed channel.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Claim your handle once, link your socials, and add friends everywhere.","zh":"索取您的账号一次，链接您的社交媒体，并在任何地方添加朋友。"},{"en":"They find your public key automatically.","zh":"他们会自动找到您的公钥。"},{"en":"Every app you share becomes a sealed channel.","zh":"您共享的每个应用程序都会成为一个密封的通道。"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Off the grid</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Off the grid","zh":"脱离电网"}]},{"html_en":"<p>No handle, no sign-in, nothing to join. Generate keys on your device and trade invites directly with the people you trust. We never even learn you exist.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"No handle, no sign-in, nothing to join.","zh":"没有句柄，没有登录，没有任何可加入的内容。"},{"en":"Generate keys on your device and trade invites directly with the people you trust.","zh":"在您的设备上生成密钥并直接与您信任的人交易邀请。"},{"en":"We never even learn you exist.","zh":"我们甚至不知道你的存在。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>FAQ</p>","sentences":[]},{"html_en":"<h2>Frequently asked questions.</h2>","sentences":[{"en":"Frequently asked questions.","zh":"常见问题。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>No, and that's the whole point. Ekko is a layer over the apps you already use. Your chats stay exactly where they are. The words inside them just stop being readable to anyone but the person you wrote to.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"No, and that's the whole point.","zh":"不，这就是重点。"},{"en":"Ekko is a layer over the apps you already use.","zh":"Ekko 是您已使用的应用程序之上的一层。"},{"en":"Your chats stay exactly where they are.","zh":"您的聊天内容完全保留在原来的位置。"},{"en":"The words inside them just stop being readable to anyone but the person you wrote to.","zh":"除了你写信的人之外，任何人都无法阅读其中的文字。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Handles and public keys. That's the entire directory. Your private keys are generated and stay on your device, and your messages travel through your apps as sealed ciphertext, never through us.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Handles and public keys.","zh":"句柄和公钥。"},{"en":"That's the entire directory.","zh":"这就是整个目录。"},{"en":"Your private keys are generated and stay on your device, and your messages travel through your apps as sealed ciphertext, never through us.","zh":"您的私钥将生成并保留在您的设备上，您的消息以密封密文的形式通过您的应用程序传输，而不是通过我们。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Only if you want one. Claim a handle so friends find your key automatically, or stay off the grid entirely and trade invites by hand. Both modes are first-class.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Only if you want one.","zh":"只要你想要一个。"},{"en":"Claim a handle so friends find your key automatically, or stay off the grid entirely and trade invites by hand.","zh":"索取一个句柄，以便朋友自动找到您的密钥，或者完全远离网络并手动交易邀请。"},{"en":"Both modes are first-class.","zh":"两种模式都是一流的。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Every message is sealed with a hybrid of X25519 and ML-KEM-768 with XChaCha20-Poly1305. Anything recorded today stays unreadable, even to a future quantum computer. The protocol spec is public.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Every message is sealed with a hybrid of X25519 and ML-KEM-768 with XChaCha20-Poly1305.","zh":"每条消息均采用 X25519 和 ML-KEM-768 与 XChaCha20-Poly1305 的混合密封。"},{"en":"Anything recorded today stays unreadable, even to a future quantum computer.","zh":"今天记录的任何内容都无法读取，即使对于未来的量子计算机也是如此。"},{"en":"The protocol spec is public.","zh":"协议规范是公开的。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>The ones you already have. Ekko rides on top of Instagram, WhatsApp, Telegram, X, Messenger and more: it starts in your browser and unlocks messengers in waves, with your phone's keyboard next. Subscribe to the newsletter and you're first to hear as each one lights up.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"The ones you already have.","zh":"那些你已经拥有的。"},{"en":"Ekko rides on top of Instagram, WhatsApp, Telegram, X, Messenger and more: it starts in your browser and unlocks messengers in waves, with your phone's keyboard next.","zh":"Ekko 运行在 Instagram、WhatsApp、Telegram、X、Messenger 等之上：它在您的浏览器中启动，然后依次解锁手机键盘。"},{"en":"Subscribe to the newsletter and you're first to hear as each one lights up.","zh":"订阅新闻通讯，当每个新闻通讯亮起时，您都会第一个听到。"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Yes. The code is open source, so the basic functionality stays available forever.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Yes.","zh":"是的。"},{"en":"The code is open source, so the basic functionality stays available forever.","zh":"该代码是开源的，因此基本功能永远可用。"}]},{"html_en":"<h2>Take privacy back.</h2>","sentences":[{"en":"Take privacy back.","zh":"夺回隐私。"}]}],"translated":true,"content_html_zh":"<div class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div tabindex=\"-1\" id=\"main-content\">\n\n  <!-- ── Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->\n  <section>\n    \n    <p>后量子加密，就在您已​​经输入的地方。 没有新的信使，也没有人可以谈论切换。</p>\n    \n\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ── Product ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->\n  <section id=\"see\">\n    <figure>\n      \n      <figcaption>私人消息，就在您已​​经聊天的地方。</figcaption>\n      <p>动画演示：Ekko 在发送者的设备上密封一对一消息，并在接收者的聊天中打开它。</p>\n    </figure>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ── The wire interlude: one message, seen twice ─────────── -->\n  \n\n  <!-- ── Works with (official marks, nominative \"works with\" use) ── -->\n  <section aria-label=\"Works with the apps you already use\">\n    <div>\n        <ul>\n        <li>Instagram</li>\n        <li>WhatsApp</li>\n        <li>电报</li>\n        <li>留言</li>\n        <li><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"X\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M18.901 1.153h3.68l-8.04 9.19L24 22.846h-7.406l-5.8-7.584-6.638 7.584H.474l8.6-9.83L0 1.154h7.594l5.243 6.932ZM17.61 20.644h2.039L6.486 3.24H4.298Z\" /></svg><span>X</span></li>\n        <li>信使</li>\n        <li>不和谐</li>\n        <li><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Viber\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M11.4 0C9.473.028 5.333.344 3.02 2.467 1.302 4.187.696 6.7.633 9.817.57 12.933.488 18.776 6.12 20.36h.003l-.004 2.416s-.037.977.61 1.177c.777.242 1.234-.5 1.98-1.302.407-.44.972-1.084 1.397-1.58 3.85.326 6.812-.416 7.15-.525.776-.252 5.176-.816 5.892-6.657.74-6.02-.36-9.83-2.34-11.546-.596-.55-3.006-2.3-8.375-2.323 0 0-.395-.025-1.037-.017zm.058 1.693c.545-.004.88.017.88.017 4.542.02 6.717 1.388 7.222 1.846 1.675 1.435 2.53 4.868 1.906 9.897v.002c-.604 4.878-4.174 5.184-4.832 5.395-.28.09-2.882.737-6.153.524 0 0-2.436 2.94-3.197 3.704-.12.12-.26.167-.352.144-.13-.033-.166-.188-.165-.414l.02-4.018c-4.762-1.32-4.485-6.292-4.43-8.895.054-2.604.543-4.738 1.996-6.173 1.96-1.773 5.474-2.018 7.11-2.03zm.38 2.602c-.167 0-.303.135-.304.302 0 .167.133.303.3.305 1.624.01 2.946.537 4.028 1.592 1.073 1.046 1.62 2.468 1.633 4.334.002.167.14.3.307.3.166-.002.3-.138.3-.304-.014-1.984-.618-3.596-1.816-4.764-1.19-1.16-2.692-1.753-4.447-1.765zm-3.96.695c-.19-.032-.4.005-.616.117l-.01.002c-.43.247-.816.562-1.146.932-.002.004-.006.004-.008.008-.267.323-.42.638-.46.948-.008.046-.01.093-.007.14 0 .136.022.27.065.4l.013.01c.135.48.473 1.276 1.205 2.604.42.768.903 1.5 1.446 2.186.27.344.56.673.87.984l.132.132c.31.308.64.6.984.87.686.543 1.418 1.027 2.186 1.447 1.328.733 2.126 1.07 2.604 1.206l.01.014c.13.042.265.064.402.063.046.002.092 0 .138-.008.31-.036.627-.19.948-.46.004 0 .003-.002.008-.005.37-.33.683-.72.93-1.148l.003-.01c.225-.432.15-.842-.18-1.12-.004 0-.698-.58-1.037-.83-.36-.255-.73-.492-1.113-.71-.51-.285-1.032-.106-1.248.174l-.447.564c-.23.283-.657.246-.657.246-3.12-.796-3.955-3.955-3.955-3.955s-.037-.426.248-.656l.563-.448c.277-.215.456-.737.17-1.248-.217-.383-.454-.756-.71-1.115-.25-.34-.826-1.033-.83-1.035-.137-.165-.31-.265-.502-.297zm4.49.88c-.158.002-.29.124-.3.282-.01.167.115.312.282.324 1.16.085 2.017.466 2.645 1.15.63.688.93 1.524.906 2.57-.002.168.13.306.3.31.166.003.305-.13.31-.297.025-1.175-.334-2.193-1.067-2.994-.74-.81-1.777-1.253-3.05-1.346h-.024zm.463 1.63c-.16.002-.29.127-.3.287-.008.167.12.31.288.32.523.028.875.175 1.113.422.24.245.388.62.416 1.164.01.167.15.295.318.287.167-.008.295-.15.287-.317-.03-.644-.215-1.178-.58-1.557-.367-.378-.893-.574-1.52-.607h-.018z\" /></svg><span>Viber</span></li>\n        </ul>\n        \n      </div>\n    <p>跨越你所有的使者。 今天在您的浏览器中。 接下来在你的键盘上。</p>\n  </section>\n\n\n  <!-- ── How ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->\n  <section id=\"how\">\n    <p>它是如何运作的</p>\n    <h2>三步。 然后忘记它的存在。</h2>\n    <div>\n      <div>\n        <p>1</p>\n        <h3>认领你的句柄</h3>\n        <p>密钥在您的设备上生成，并由您的密码密封。 抓住@you，或者保持完全匿名。</p>\n        \n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <p>2</p>\n        <h3>同步您的人员</h3>\n        <p>您的私钥永远不会离开您的设备。 Ekko 仅发布人们联系您所需的公钥。 它永远不会上传打开您的消息的密钥。</p>\n        \n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <p>3</p>\n        <h3>写下你们已经聊天的地方</h3>\n        <p>标记位于盒子的末端。 它会说出要密封的对象，检查他们的密钥，然后将这些单词加密。 今天在您的浏览器中，接下来在您的键盘中。</p>\n        \n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <hr>\n\n  <!-- ── Two modes ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->\n  <section id=\"modes\">\n    <p>两种使用方式</p>\n    <h2>索取句柄。 或者留下一个幽灵。</h2>\n    <div>\n      <div>\n        <h3>@你，无处不在</h3>\n        <p>索取您的账号一次，链接您的社交媒体，并在任何地方添加朋友。 他们会自动找到您的公钥。 您共享的每个应用程序都会成为一个密封的通道。</p>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <h3>脱离电网</h3>\n        <p>没有句柄，没有登录，没有任何可加入的内容。 在您的设备上生成密钥并直接与您信任的人交易邀请。 我们甚至不知道你的存在。</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <hr>\n\n  <!-- ── FAQ ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->\n  <section id=\"faq\">\n    <p>FAQ</p>\n    <h2>常见问题。</h2>\n    <div>\n      <details name=\"faq\">\n        <summary>Is Ekko another messenger I have to move people to?</summary>\n        <p>不，这就是重点。 Ekko 是您已使用的应用程序之上的一层。 您的聊天内容完全保留在原来的位置。 除了你写信的人之外，任何人都无法阅读其中的文字。</p>\n      </details>\n      <details name=\"faq\">\n        <summary>What do Ekko's servers actually see?</summary>\n        <p>句柄和公钥。 这就是整个目录。 您的私钥将生成并保留在您的设备上，您的消息以密封密文的形式通过您的应用程序传输，而不是通过我们。</p>\n      </details>\n      <details name=\"faq\">\n        <summary>Do I need an account?</summary>\n        <p>只要你想要一个。 索取一个句柄，以便朋友自动找到您的密钥，或者完全远离网络并手动交易邀请。 两种模式都是一流的。</p>\n      </details>\n      <details name=\"faq\">\n        <summary>What does \"post-quantum\" mean here?</summary>\n        <p>每条消息均采用 X25519 和 ML-KEM-768 与 XChaCha20-Poly1305 的混合密封。 今天记录的任何内容都无法读取，即使对于未来的量子计算机也是如此。 协议规范是公开的。</p>\n      </details>\n      <details name=\"faq\">\n        <summary>Which apps does Ekko work with?</summary>\n        <p>那些你已经拥有的。 Ekko 运行在 Instagram、WhatsApp、Telegram、X、Messenger 等之上：它在您的浏览器中启动，然后依次解锁手机键盘。 订阅新闻通讯，当每个新闻通讯亮起时，您都会第一个听到。</p>\n      </details>\n      <details name=\"faq\">\n        <summary>Is it free?</summary>\n        <p>是的。 该代码是开源的，因此基本功能永远可用。</p>\n      </details>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <hr>\n\n  <!-- ── Get Ekko ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->\n  <section id=\"get\">\n    <h2>夺回隐私。</h2>\n    \n    \n  </section>\n\n</div></div>"}